FBIS4-61566 "drsov089_a_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-089 Daily Report 8 May 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Border Post Shelled From Tajik Territory Border Post Shelled From Tajik Territory LD0805110694 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1000 GMT 8 May 94 LD0805110694 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] INTERFAX reports that a post of Russian border guards at the 12th outpost of the Moscow border detachment came under mortar fire on Saturday. The fire came from Tajik territory. There are no casualties among the Russian border guards. Up to 10 groups of militants have accumulated in the rear of the 11th and 12th outposts of the Moscow border detachment. The command of the Russian border troops in Tajikistan is taking urgent measures to repel a possible attack on border detachments and military settlements.
